folder: Macombs Road & Mt. Eden Avenue, Bronx, NY
original_title: Bronx: Macombs Road - Mt. Eden Avenue
text:
(1) 1585 Macombs Road, west side at Mt. Eden Avenue, showing the Townsend Poole Cottage. It was built in 1782. Here Lieutenant Peary's Eskimos were for a time lodged. A five-story apartment house was later erected here.

Gift of Randall Comfort  1899

(2,3) The same, years later  1915
